===鑽禧球場===
鑽禧球場是聖安德魯斯第三個作為[[英國高爾夫球公開賽|英國高爾夫球公開賽]]會場使用的球場。球場得名於[[維多利亞女王|維多利亞女王]]在1897年的[[鑽禧|鑽禧]]慶典<ref>{{cite web | title = Jubilee Course at St Andrews | date = 2007 | url = http://www.standrews.org.uk/golf/the_courses/jubilee_course.html | format = web | access-date = 2008-07-09 | archive-date = 2008-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080510134950/http://www.standrews.org.uk/golf/the_courses/jubilee_course.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。鑽禧球場最初是面向女性及新手的球場，但現在已成為聖安德魯林克斯最難的球場之一。該球場通常作為青年和業餘測試賽，以及{{link-en|聖安德魯林克斯盃|St Andrews Links Trophy}}的比賽場地<ref>{{cite web | title = Jubilee Course at St Andrews | date = 2007 | url = http://www.standrews.org.uk/golf/the_courses/jubilee_course.html | format = web | access-date = 2008-02-16 | archive-date = 2008-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080510134950/http://www.standrews.org.uk/golf/the_courses/jubilee_course.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

鑽禧球場最初是一個12洞球場<ref name="beg">{{Cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1987-12-06/sports/sp-27177_1_st-andrews-golf-club|title=Where the Games Began|access-date=2008-06-09|date=1987-12-06|author=Charles Hillinger|work=The Los Angeles Times|archive-date=2012-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022005648/http://articles.latimes.com/1987-12-06/sports/sp-27177_1_st-andrews-golf-club|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在1905年擴張為18洞球場。現在鑽禧球場全長6,745碼。鑽禧球場是蘇格蘭數座面臨[[侵蝕作用|侵蝕作用]]威脅的球場之一<ref name="usat">{{Cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/sports/golf/british01/stories/2001-07-18-focus-erosion.htm|title=Erosion Threatens Legendary British Golf Courses|access-date=2008-06-09|date=2001-07-17|author=Ellen Hale|work=USA Today|archive-date=2009-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611121513/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/golf/british01/stories/2001-07-18-focus-erosion.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

